    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/caaf151ebb4c6e76a8db25fe8dcb45b7.avif?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=120 /></span><strong>Play the free demo of this turn-based pirate strategy game!</strong> Command your ship in intense naval battles, make bold decisions, and outsmart rival captains. This is just a glimpse—<strong>the full game offers even more challenges, depth, customization, and chaos on the high seas!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/c6ba4f615d52ffda86f26f7bf13f4741.webp?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/eb7e4f9746bca50eb9d01f19a4665d62.poster.avif?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/eb7e4f9746bca50eb9d01f19a4665d62.webm?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/eb7e4f9746bca50eb9d01f19a4665d62.mp4?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Execute moves simultaneously for strategic prediction and positioning.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate obstacles and leverage the environment to your advantage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize the wind to reduce movement costs when sailing with it, avoid the storm or use it to escape chasing players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fear the ever-growing curse of the sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/6e271bd38df06e7289a521a734512ef4.webp?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/0fbcb34dd737527d6b69fb18b7c2d362.poster.avif?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/0fbcb34dd737527d6b69fb18b7c2d362.webm?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/0fbcb34dd737527d6b69fb18b7c2d362.mp4?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick between various upgrades to increase your power.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash environmental chaos causing misfortune throughout the seven seas, giving you both advantages and disadvantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steer the course of battle by picking between special mythic perks with even greater powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MORE TO COME IN THE FULL RELEASE..</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/2f320a51f8b666169365b51387a4ad28.webp?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/405353f2d53ca9a32894a87b9d210b88.poster.avif?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/405353f2d53ca9a32894a87b9d210b88.webm?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/405353f2d53ca9a32894a87b9d210b88.mp4?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your crew, giving them tasks like fishing, treasure hunting, and resource gathering.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your ship and customize components for increased sail speed, greater defenses, better vision, and faster repairs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick and play a role in your fleet and contribute to a strongly drafted crew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/c1e7bd29249dfe520af6ca459c672baa.webp?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/7ae42e607b28440921f83e1fc61fbc04.poster.avif?t=1758045870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/7ae42e607b28440921f83e1fc61fbc04.webm?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256770/extras/7ae42e607b28440921f83e1fc61fbc04.mp4?t=1758045870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge epic bosses, wield their powers, and unlock abilities to cause havoc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight sea monsters for valuable upgrades and significant buffs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat AI fleets and mighty pirate ships, or invite them to battle on your side for a good deal.</p></li></ul>",
